======================
htlc 使用流程
======================

---
生成随机secret
---
iristool debug rand-bech32
（secret）c11253563a79bc91d35070834034f9896f27a6bfa2938ede3cd1acff3a57d5dc

---
通过secret生成hash-lock (注意：带不带timestamp结果是不一样的， timestamp是适配币安)
---
iristool debug hash-lock c11253563a79bc91d35070834034f9896f27a6bfa2938ede3cd1acff3a57d5dc 1580000000
ff9878983871e35a4b267e9d38c73f13d3f5a2736dda1bd066e95a27d825acd6

iristool debug hash-lock 5aa2bbf19ef41b0616908cd4bc81f137f92890f50ea12e17f13264539ca00c74
72f5ba7d4b2027b86415a757164013f4b797f0b14ec3a5a06ddf9dc849593a7e


======================
Create htlc
======================
//注意：因为本链 所以other-chain这个暂时00
echo 1234567890 | iriscli htlc create --from=v0 --receiver=faa1lcuw6ewd2gfxap37sejewmta205sgssmv5fnju  --amount=10iris --time-lock=50 --timestamp=1580000000 --hash-lock=ff9878983871e35a4b267e9d38c73f13d3f5a2736dda1bd066e95a27d825acd6 --receiver-on-other-chain=00 --fee=0.3iris --chain-id=shilei-qa --commit


======================
查询  query-htlc
======================

iriscli htlc query-htlc ff9878983871e35a4b267e9d38c73f13d3f5a2736dda1bd066e95a27d825acd6


======================
声明所有 claim
======================

echo 1234567890 | iriscli htlc claim --hash-lock=ff9878983871e35a4b267e9d38c73f13d3f5a2736dda1bd066e95a27d825acd6 --secret=c11253563a79bc91d35070834034f9896f27a6bfa2938ede3cd1acff3a57d5dc --from=v0 --fee=0.3iris --chain-id=shilei-qa --commit


======================
取回过期  htlc refund
======================

echo 1234567890 | iriscli htlc refund --from=v0 --hash-lock=ff9878983871e35a4b267e9d38c73f13d3f5a2736dda1bd066e95a27d825acd6 --fee=0.3iris --chain-id=shilei-qa --commit